dc_description_s: This point shapefile represents individual addresses in Placer County California. Address point include APN, street number, street name, street type. Efforts are made to place the point at the location of the structure. However, not all locations will be located at the location of the structure. Placer County Geographic Information Systems. (2020). Address Points, Placer County, California, 2020. Placer County Geographic Information Systems. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/ny874fh6077 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
